item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: http://localhost/clinicweb.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

"Why Choose Indira Physio Clinic?"

🌟 Discover Excellence in Jaipur

Welcome to Indira Physio Clinic, the epitome of physiotherapy excellence in Jaipur. Recognized as the best in the city, we take pride in our commitment to providing unparalleled care. Trust us to be your partner in health, where your well-being is our top priority.

🌟 Caring Beyond the Treatment Room: “Patient-Centric Care.” 

At Indira Physio Clinic, our dedication goes beyond treatment. We believe in patient-centric care, ensuring that you feel supported, understood, and cared for throughout your wellness journey. Your comfort, both physically and emotionally, matters to us.

🌟 Convenience at Your Doorstep: “Home Visit Services”

We understand that your well-being is a priority, and sometimes that means bringing care to your doorstep. Dr. Vaibhav Parashar extends our services with home visits, ensuring you receive the expert care you need in the comfort of your home.

🌟 Comprehensive Physiotherapy Services

Indira Physio Clinic offers a range of comprehensive physiotherapy services tailored to your unique needs. From Cervical and Lumber Spondylosis to heel pain and sports injury treatments, our expert doctor is dedicated to enhancing your overall well-being through specialized care.

🌟 Experience Expert Care in Our Clinic

Step into a world of healing at Indira Physio Clinic. Our state-of-the-art facility is designed to provide a comfortable and tranquil environment for your physiotherapy treatments. Trust our experienced physiotherapist to guide you on your journey to recovery.

🌟 Access Expert Care In Jaipur

Indira Physio Clinic goes beyond boundaries to ensure you have access to expert care. Experience the convenience of online consultations from the comfort of your home. Additionally, for those who prefer in-person care, Dr. Vaibhav Parashar offers home visit services, bringing our expertise to your doorstep.

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Elevating Lives Through Expert Care

Welcome to Indira Physio Clinic, your gateway to unrivaled physiotherapy in Jaipur. Led by the esteemed Dr. Vaibhav Parashar, our clinic is a beacon of healing, where personalized care meets advanced treatments to rejuvenate your body and spirit.

Services That Transform :)

Cervical and Lumbar Spondylosis Treatment:

Find relief from neck and lower back discomfort with our specialized treatments targeting cervical and lumbar spondylosis. Our expert physiotherapist craft personalized plans to alleviate pain and enhance mobility.

Frozen Shoulder Rehabilitation:

Regain shoulder mobility and overcome the constraints of a frozen shoulder with our targeted rehabilitation programs. Our therapists guide you through exercises and therapies to restore flexibility and function.

Arthritis Management:

Combat arthritis with our comprehensive management programs. Indira Physio Clinic offers specialized treatments to reduce pain, improve joint function, and enhance your overall quality of life.

Sprain and Strain Therapy:

Recover swiftly from sprains and strains with our focused physiotherapy. Our team designs tailored treatment plans to alleviate pain, reduce inflammation, and accelerate the healing process.

IFT, Ultrasonic Therapy, and Muscle Stimulator:

Experience advanced physiotherapy techniques with Indira Physio Clinic. Our services include Interferential Therapy (IFT), Ultrasonic Therapy, and Muscle Stimulator treatments for targeted relief and muscle rehabilitation.

Know More About Our Services 0 Different Services

Address

24, Agrasen Nagar (Extension), Near Mahesh Nagar Railway Crossing, Jaipur , Rajasthan

item.title: Our Services
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
We facilitate rehabilitation for:

Cervical and Lumber Spondylosis

Indulge in specialized treatments crafted to alleviate discomfort associated with Cervical and Lumbar Spondylosis. Our physiotherapist Dr. Vaibhav Parashar(BPT) design personalized plans for effective pain management, prioritizing your unique needs.

Frozen Shoulder

Embark on a journey to regain shoulder mobility with our targeted rehabilitation programs for frozen shoulder. Our therapists guide you through exercises and therapies, ensuring a comprehensive approach to restore flexibility and function.

Arthritis

Combat arthritis with our comprehensive management programs. Indira Physio Clinic offers specialized treatments to reduce pain, improve joint function, and enhance your overall quality of life. Our focus is on personalized care tailored to your specific arthritis needs.

Sprain and Strain

Swiftly recover from sprains and strains with our focused physiotherapy. Our team designs tailored treatment plans to alleviate pain, reduce inflammation, and accelerate the healing process, ensuring you return to optimal functionality.

IFT, Ultrasonic Therapy, and Muscle Stimulator

Experience advanced physiotherapy techniques with Indira Physio Clinic. Our services include Interferential Therapy (IFT), Ultrasonic Therapy, and Muscle Stimulator treatments for targeted relief and muscle rehabilitation. These modalities bring a holistic approach to your recovery.

Exercise Therapy

Unlock your body’s potential with our exercise therapy programs. Tailored to your specific needs, our exercises enhance strength, flexibility, and overall physical well-being. Experience the transformative power of therapeutic exercises at Indira Physio Clinic.

Tennis Elbow

Get back to your activities without the pain of tennis elbow. Our specialized treatments focus on reducing inflammation and strengthening the affected area for a speedy recovery. Regain pain-free movement with our expert care.

Heel Pain

Bid farewell to heel pain with our effective management programs. Our physiotherapists address the root causes of heel pain, providing relief and promoting long-term comfort. Walk with ease and comfort with our dedicated heel pain management.

Osteoarthritis Care

Navigate osteoarthritis with our comprehensive care plans. Indira Physio Clinic offers specialized treatments to manage symptoms, improve joint function, and enhance your overall quality of life. Our dedicated care aims to transform your osteoarthritis journey.

SWD (Shortwave Diathermy) and Paraffin Wax Therapy

ndulge in therapeutic warmth with our SWD and Paraffin Wax Therapy. These treatments aid in pain relief, muscle relaxation, and enhanced circulation for a soothing experience. Experience the comforting warmth of therapeutic modalities at Indira Physio Clinic.
